<section
    id="inicio"
    class="relative
    w-full
    overflow-hidden
    pt-24
    pb-32
    sm:pt-32
    sm:pb-40
    lg:pt-40
    lg:pb-48"
>
    <!-- Dynamic Background -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
        <!-- Overlay Gradient - Darker and more neutral -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-mga-dark/80 z-10"></div>
        <img
            src="/assets/img/hero.png"
            alt="Ingeniería y Construcción"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        />
    </div>

    <div class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 relative z-20">
        <div class="max-w-4xl">
            <h1
                class="text-3xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl xl:text-8xl font-bold text-white leading-[1.1] mb-8 animate-fade-up tracking-tight drop-shadow-xl max-w-[100vw]"
                style="animation-delay: 0.1s;"
            >
                Consultoría que <br />
                <span class="text-mga-blue">Transforma</span>
                Futuros
            </h1>

            <p
                class="text-slate-200 text-lg md:text-2xl mb-10 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl font-light animate-fade-up text-pretty"
                style="animation-delay: 0.2s;"
            >
                Somos especialistas en consultoría electromecánica y gestión de
                proyectos, con más de 14 años de experiencia brindando
                soluciones técnicas confiables para el sector público y privado,
                cumpliendo los más altos estándares de calidad y normativa.
            </p>

            <div
                class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5 animate-fade-up"
                style="animation-delay: 0.3s;"
            >
                <a
                    href="/portafolio"
                    class="group relative px-8 py-4 bg-mga-orange hover:bg-orange-600 rounded-full font-bold text-white shadow-xl shadow-mga-orange/20 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 overflow-hidden w-full sm:w-auto text-center"
                >
                    <span class="relative z-10 flex items-center gap-3">
                        Ver Portafolio <i
                            class="fas fa-arrow-right group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
                        ></i>
                    </span>
                    <!-- Shine Effect -->
                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/20 to-transparent -translate-x-full group-hover:animate-[shimmer_1.5s_infinite]"
                    >
                    </div>
                </a>
                <a
                    href="#nosotros"
                    class="px-8 py-4 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 rounded-full font-bold text-white hover:bg-white/10 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-mga-blue/50 w-full sm:w-auto text-center"
                >
                    Conoce Más
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Decorative Elements -->
    <div
        class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-1/3 h-full bg-gradient-to-l from-mga-blue/20 to-transparent z-0 pointer-events-none"
    >
    </div>
    <div
        class="absolute -bottom-32 -left-32 w-96 h-96 bg-mga-blue/30 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none"
    >
    </div>

    <!-- Floating Stats or Visual Element (Optional - simplified for now) -->

    <!-- Scroll Indicator -->
    <div
        class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce text-white/50 z-20 cursor-pointer hover:text-mga-orange transition-colors"
        onclick="document.getElementById('nosotros').scrollIntoView({behavior: 'smooth'})"
    >
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down text-2xl"></i>
    </div>
</section>
